title: Toaru Kagaku no Railgun - DL - Toaru Soushuuhen (Doujinshi)
description:
Please consider chapters in this Manga to be modified. Chapters that appear in D.L. Action Compilation & Rough Sketch Compilation are the original releases.

This entry is for the official tankoubon release. (Pages removed by author for this Compilation... Mainly sketches, inserts, backs and a few illustrations) Covers have been preserved since there are no color versions available for the soushuuhen release.

Missing Rough Sketch 46 & 62
